g = Graph()
original = g
g -= Graph()
assert g.triples == []
assert g.top is None
assert g is original
g = Graph([('a', ':instance', 'alpha'), ('a', ':ARG', 'b'), ('b',
    ':instance', 'beta')])
original = g
g -= Graph([('a', ':instance', 'alpha'), ('a', ':ARG', 'b')])
assert g.triples == [('b', ':instance', 'beta')]
assert g.top == 'b'
assert g is original
